   Digital Equipment Corp. says it has struck a deal
to market personal computers manufactured by Tandy Corp., a move
that takes the heat off Digital to produce a personal computer of
its own.
   Tandy will make personal computers to Digital's specifications,
which Digital will market and sell under its brand, Digital said
Thursday.
