   Stock prices rose slightly at midday Friday.
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was up 2
points, or 0.1 percent, at 1,840.9 around 1 p.m. local time.
   Volume totaled 373.1 million shares, compared with 356.1 million
